OL,3,CTwo thirds of Brits experience health-
OL,4,Crelated anxiety
OL,6,FExclusive polling for Good Morning
OL,7,FBritain has revealed the extent of
OL,8,Fhealth-related anxiety. Words and
OL,9,Freporting by GMB reporter Philip Sime,
OL,10,Fand Producer Susannah Thraves
OL,12,FTwo-thirds of Brits suffer from health-
OL,13,Frelated anxiety, an exclusive poll for
OL,14,FGood Morning Britain has revealed.
OL,16,FWhile many of us are anxious about our
OL,17,Fhealth, for some, it can be
OL,18,Fdebilitating. An illness in itself,
OL,19,Fknown as health anxiety.
