OL,4,Crelated anxiety
OL,6,FHealth anxiety is diagnosed when a
OL,7,Fperson spends so much time worrying
OL,8,Fthat they are ill, or are going to get
OL,9,Fill, that it takes over their life.
OL,11,F"You're checking how you're feeling,
OL,12,Fhow you're thinking, is your skin
OL,13,Ftingly, is that mole normal, it's just
OL,14,Fthis constant compulsion," Vicky told
OL,15,FGood Morning Britain.
OL,17,F"You do know deep down that you're
OL,18,Fbeing anxious, but there is always
OL,19,Fthis doubt in your brain that's going,
OL,20,F'no, no you must go see your doctor.'
OL,21,FIt's a vicious cycle," she said.
