OL,6,FWhile it's been an issue since long
OL,7,Fbefore the internet age, doctors tell
OL,8,Fus they are seeing an increase in
OL,9,Fpatients presenting with health
OL,10,Fanxiety. And they cite the online
OL,11,Fworld we live in, which gives us
OL,12,Fanswers to our symptoms at the click
OL,13,Fof a button, as contributing to the
OL,14,Frise.
OL,16,FSo we wanted to see for ourselves.
OL,18,FAn IPSOS survey exclusively for Good
OL,19,FMorning Britain has found:
