OL,6,FAt the height of her condition ten
OL,7,Fyears ago, Vicky used online searches,
OL,8,Fforums and social media to obsessively
OL,9,Flook up symptoms. Thanks to Cognitive
OL,10,FBehaviour Therapy, which she says was
OL,11,F"life-changing", her anxiety is now
OL,12,Funder control.
OL,14,FShe has since written about her
OL,15,Fcondition and says that people message
OL,16,Fher daily to share their own stories.
OL,18,FVicky told us that she is grateful
OL,19,Fthat her experience came before the AI
OL,20,Fboom, as she thinks she would have
OL,21,Fbeen "ten times worse".
