OL,6,FBut what do doctors think?
OL,8,FDr Amir Khan is an NHS GP in Bradford.
OL,9,FMultiple patients a week tell him that
OL,10,Fthey've looked up symptoms on AI.
OL,12,F"My worry with AI is that it is not
OL,13,Fdesigned to reassure. It is not
OL,14,Fdesigned to weigh up the nuances that
OL,15,Fare needed in a conversation. It is
OL,16,Fcertainly not designed to manage
OL,17,Funcertainty," Dr Khan told Good
OL,18,FMorning Britain.
