OL,6,F"Instead, it puts the most clicked
OL,7,Fthing on the top of a search model and
OL,8,Foften that is the worst case scenario
OL,9,Fso it can add a lot to patient
OL,10,Fanxiety," Dr Khan added.
OL,12,FHe wants people to always speak to
OL,13,Ftheir GP if they are concerned about
OL,14,Fsymptoms, rather than rely on the
OL,15,F"doctor" on the internet.
OL,17,FA study in 2017 estimated that the NHS
OL,18,Fcould save more than #420m a year if
OL,19,Fit offered treatment for health
OL,20,Fanxiety.
