OL,6,FEmeritus Professor in Community
OL,7,FPsychiatry, Peter Tyrer, an author in
OL,8,Fthat study, says the cost would likely
OL,9,Fbe higher now.
OL,11,FAn expert in health anxiety for forty
OL,12,Fyears, he would like national
OL,13,Fguidelines to be updated and for NHS
OL,14,Fhospitals to bring in nurses who are
OL,15,Ftrained to treat health anxiety.
OL,16,FAnything less, he thinks, would just
OL,17,Fbe a plaster over a huge problem.
