OL,6,F"It's very serious and it's been
OL,7,Frumbling on the surface for many years
OL,8,Fand it's now coming to the top,"
OL,9,FProfessor Tyrer told Good Morning
OL,10,FBritain.
OL,12,F"We almost got the NHS to adopt a
OL,13,Ftraining programme but we haven't got
OL,14,Fthere yet. We can have treatments
OL,15,Favailable so that the people who come
OL,16,Fup repeatedly with health anxiety can
OL,17,Fhave an intervention. Once we've given
OL,18,Fthat treatment, it tends to last," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
