OL,6,FThe National Institute for Health and
OL,7,FCare Excellence (NICE), which provides
OL,8,Fnational guidance and advice to
OL,9,Fimprove health, told us that they are
OL,10,Fcurrently reviewing health anxiety as
OL,11,Fa topic for potential new guidance.
OL,12,FThey said that this review "will be
OL,13,Fconsidered by our Prioritisation Board
OL,14,Fin due course."
OL,16,FExperts tell us this review into
OL,17,Fhealth anxiety can't come soon enough.
OL,19,FFor Vicky, it's vital that we treat
OL,20,Fthe cause of the problem, not just the
OL,21,Fsymptoms.
